headline: Cboe Upgraded To Buy: Deutsche Bank Sees Strong Revenue Growth And Margin Gains Through 2025
summary: Deutsche Bank analyst Brian Bedell upgraded Cboe Global Markets, Inc. (BATS:CBOE) to Buy from Hold and raised the price target to $222. The analyst’s bullish stance reflects their updated outlook that CBOE will sustain strong revenue growth through at least 2025.
